Hi please make a note of below commands.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
To set proxy for npm the commands:
'npm config set proxy http://username:password@proxyaddress:port/'
'npm config set http-proxy http://username:password@proxyaddress:port/'
'npm config set https-proxy http://username:password@proxyaddress:port/'
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
To unset proxy for npm the commands:
'npm config set proxy null'
'npm config set http-proxy null'
'npm config set https-proxy null'
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
To set proxy for git 
git config --global http.proxy http://username:password@proxyaddress:port/
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
To unset proxy for git
git config --global --list
git config --global --unset http.proxy
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
